Oyo State Police Command yesterday  confirmed the killing of one Maduabuchi Onwuamanam, a businessman, who was shot dead by some gunmen. It was gathered that Onwuamanam was killed by the hoodlums around 10pm on Saturday. The businessman, 51, was allegedly attacked in the Oremeji Mokola area of Ibadan. The wife of the deceased, Christianah Onwuamanam reported the matter at the police station. Police spokesman Adewale Osifeso confirmed the incident. He said “The unfortunate incident was reported to the Police at about 2210hrs on Saturday 29th May 2021 by the wife of the deceased, one Christianah Owuamanam.